{"id": 1299, "genre": 1001, "title": "今年你都见过哪些“自说自话”？", "description": "真的是......活在自己的世界中。（题图来自：Riikka Laakso）", "record_count": 3192, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161030152658O3SetnVFUZqYis6H.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-17T03:00:48Z", "options": [{"id": 134656, "content": "电影人吹嘘自己的烂片有多好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804214}, {"id": 128512, "content": "在微博上坚持不懈@别人，但从未有回应", "image": null, "praise_count": 69, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 134658, "content": "萌真人cp", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820494}, {"id": 134659, "content": "特朗普：白宫是我住的最小的房子了，当总统好累。\n具体的话记不太清了，不过大致是这个意思", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788971}, {"id": 134660, "content": "没事儿，一切都不是事儿！领导来了告我一声…！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 109759}, {"id": 134662, "content": "不管你信不信，拯救世界少不了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836749}, {"id": 134663, "content": "只要我想，没有什么我做不到的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836244}, {"id": 134664, "content": "我要减肥！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836754}, {"id": 128520, "content": "五岳散人：除非是我不想，否则没有我睡不上的漂亮女孩", "image": null, "praise_count": 441, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 160521, "content": "99.99% 0kb/s那位，一般暂停再开始下载就行了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 791745}, {"id": 134666, "content": "总觉得自己做出来的东西比什么都棒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824497}, {"id": 128522, "content": "腰封上写：影响了当今整整一代人（反正我是没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 325, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 134669, "content": "我要开始学习了", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832330}, {"id": 134670, "content": "我要开始学习了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832330}, {"id": 134672, "content": "一直看到那些所谓的心灵鸡汤，现在都有点麻木了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836779}, {"id": 135184, "content": "发完装x朋友圈还得评论再解释一下生怕别人没看懂她要炫耀啥", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839314}, {"id": 134674, "content": "今天还是那么帅！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836803}, {"id": 135698, "content": "在朋友圈里写读书报告，在QQ空间写四六级英语作文。☺️", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 792021}, {"id": 134675, "content": "雾霾天气少出门", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836784}, {"id": 134677, "content": "少壮不努力，长大怪水逆", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144238}, {"id": 134678, "content": "北京这边好多人一到中年就这样...没完没了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 632962}, {"id": 134679, "content": "微商的广告……………", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 57280}, {"id": 134935, "content": "水逆来了....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838080}, {"id": 135191, "content": "老在群里水，但只有他一个人。还有水逆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839386}, {"id": 134680, "content": "无论做什么必须发动态让别人都知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826091}, {"id": 134681, "content": "看完这段（集）就睡觉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800184}, {"id": 134682, "content": "好好学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 831417}, {"id": 134684, "content": "烟厂:“吸烟有害健康”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833196}, {"id": 135452, "content": "坚持不懈的给喜欢的明星发私信", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826621}, {"id": 136732, "content": "从上班的第一天就说不在这里干了结果8年过去还在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 134941, "content": "某亲戚转发朋友圈健康文章时总是@我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249328}, {"id": 134686, "content": "小鱼不自在", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734774}, {"id": 134687, "content": "99.9%  0kb/s", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745316}, {"id": 134688, "content": "成天说“老百姓”怎么，“群众”怎么，好像说话的自己不是老百姓群众。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744307}, {"id": 134689, "content": "定一个小目标", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335818}, {"id": 134945, "content": "什么小事都得发圈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66516}, {"id": 134690, "content": "“或”怎么怎么。媒体记者报导出来都是“XX或将如何如何”，你就不能查实了再报导？我也会说，明天或将下雨。这都是废话", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744307}, {"id": 134691, "content": "我要锻炼了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836876}, {"id": 134692, "content": "不减肥的我其实挺好看", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 557898}, {"id": 134693, "content": "我绝不会出轨", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216774}, {"id": 134694, "content": "这题太简单了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 732269}, {"id": 134695, "content": "哥是你永远都得不到的男人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 241137}, {"id": 134697, "content": "什么对话都能夸下自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705337}, {"id": 134954, "content": "看着这个，自言语", "image": "img/option/option/20161118213221qoPDIN9CYfzSsMt3", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 763625}, {"id": 135978, "content": "学霸的考后感言，以及拿到分数时的谢谢大家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829603}, {"id": 134955, "content": "常在朋友圈问：有人约看某某电影吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818126}, {"id": 134700, "content": "最近有了些小秘密", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804591}, {"id": 134701, "content": "要攒钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682789}, {"id": 134702, "content": "生态化反，蒙眼狂奔的乐事薯片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130117}, {"id": 134703, "content": "沉迷学习  无法自拔", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 836993}]}